                     <interp inst="t18320105-127-person1208" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was at my window - I saw the prosecutor come out in his shirt sleeves; he had been shaving - I pursued the prisoners, and saw Messenger throw this bowl away.(Bowl produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Williams' Defence. We were not in Park-street at all.</p>
